But more importantly, who was your violin teacher anyway?

9
00:01:16,060 --> 00:01:18,050
Thank you so much, Teacher.

10
00:01:18,050 --> 00:01:22,880
Yoon Dong Yoon, if you actually taught her well, would she have needed to retake the exam four times?

11
00:01:22,880 --> 00:01:26,310
 Yeah, you weren’t that great after all! 

12
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:29,160
  - Song Ah  
 - Hmm?

13
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:31,090
 Are you happy? 

