00:02:36,250 --> 00:02:40,650
Song Ah Unni, this was your club, right? The school’s amateur orchestra?

22
00:02:40,650 --> 00:02:43,650
Yeah, the S.R.P.  back when I played full-time.

23
00:02:43,650 --> 00:02:47,790
That’s right, S.R.P.

24
00:02:47,790 --> 00:02:50,710
Why did we leave our school to perform at the arts center all the way out here?

25
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:54,020
That’s what I’m saying. At least pay for the taxi fees.

26
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:58,100
Are they saying we should just be grateful to be able to play at the arts center or what?

27
00:02:58,100 --> 00:03:01,100
As if anyone hasn't performed here yet.

28
00:03:04,790 --> 00:03:07,000
Me. I haven’t yet.

29
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:09,610
I’m totally excited right now.

30
00:03:09,610 --> 00:03:11,550
You’ve never performed here before, Unni?

31
00:03:11,550 --> 00:03:12,770
How come?

32
00:03:12,770 --> 00:03:16,380
You must have performed here with your orchestra at your performing arts high school.

33
00:03:18,630 --> 00:03:21,000
Oh, you went to an ordinary high school, right?

34
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,910
Sorry.

35
00:03:22,910 --> 00:03:24,660
It’s no big deal.

36
00:03:27,150 --> 00:03:31,250
 Rehearsal will begin. Everyone, enter the stage. 

37
