38
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:03,100
You’re 29, right?

39
00:04:03,100 --> 00:04:05,650
- Yeah.
 - You’re the same age as Park Joon Young!

40
00:04:05,650 --> 00:04:07,390
Then you must have gone to school together, right?

41
00:04:07,390 --> 00:04:09,290
During your days at music school?

42
00:04:09,290 --> 00:04:10,700
No.

43
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:15,330
We only graduated in the same year, I was still in business school then.

44
00:04:15,330 --> 00:04:17,590
- This is also my first performance. 
 - Ah.

45
